{"word":"G4065 - περιφρονέω - periphronéō - per-ee-fron-eh'-o - Despise","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περιφρονέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">periphronéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">per-ee-fron-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Despise</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அசட்டைப்பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"1. to consider or examine on all sides"},{"paragraph":"2. to set oneself in thought beyond (exalt oneself in thought above) a person or thing; to contemn, despise"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G5426 - φρονέω - phronéō - fron-eh'-o/5426\">G5426</a>; to <i>think beyond</i>, that is, <i>depreciate</i> (<i>contemn</i>): - despise.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2706/2706\">G2706</a>, <a href=\"#/G2707/2707\">G2707</a>, <a href=\"#/G4065/4065\">G4065</a>"}]}